node.text:
@chopard @diormakeup @jeanpaulgaultier Video @samvissermakeup 

I am once again honored to share a room with some of the most genius beings on the planet! I do not take this opportunity lightly - and I am just grateful to watch and learn about the arts on a first basis level. I Love you @chopard , thank you for having me walk the carpet for you! This is the greatest education of films for a girl to be blessed with. Thank you🖤

node.text:
📽🫀🧜🏽‍♀️🌎🤍
Oh!! In my wildest dreams this came true!! Somebody pinch me! 

It's been 6 years since @jpgaultierofficial launched a ready to wear collection. It is my honor, with much love and respect, to represent a brand like JPG. Especially side by side with my fellow Palestinian brother @qaherhar and the epic, and endlessly coooollll @sesay_omar .

 I will never forget this moment of shooting with you @qaherhar . It is rare in this industry to get the privilege of having so much Palestine on one job, and our connection was immediate! Weve just got that Falasteeeen energy. Thank you @_hlsa_ for bringing us together. We love you ! 

To work on projects like this, with a team of people coming from all walks of life, is the reason I continue to do this job. To highlight the beauty in diversity and then to watch it shine so bright…. Well, it just made me really proud. 

Thank you to this incredible team. I send my love to you over and over again. You are all a dream, to me. 

“Les Marins” by @charlottemwales 
styling: @georgia.pendlebury 
Hair: @yann_turchi 
Makeup: @cecileparavina 
BTS: @taqwabintali 
Nails: @lilicreuk 
Set design: @Julien_ca
ENERGY @kohlerparis <3

BY @florencetetier 

Congratulations and thank you to @antoinegagey and the entire team. I Love you x a billion ! Every single one of you!

node.text:
Daydreaming of sunny New York City days with my latest campaign for @MichaelKors, inspired by Diana Vreeland’s famous saying “The Eye Has To Travel.” 👁 

Shot by the incredibly vibrant, Fun and kind director/ person , the one and only @mattypcock !!!!! 

STYLED BY THE @luxurylaw 
Hair and makeup by @tinadidit @kristimatamoros 

We were able to lock down the whole Museum  of Natural History to ourselves, take a boat around the Statue of Liberty, float through Central Park (I always stop at my favorite ice cream truck) and eat with my girls @mayowanicholas & @hello_kijeong which was one of the most memorable days !! Veryyyy “Night at the Museum” .... matty and I have a lot of BTS pictures... do you guys wanna see!?

Thank you Michael ❤️
